And not only did they hit it, but they exceeded it.

247
00:10:37,860 --> 00:10:40,762
We actually shipped an entirely new environment set

248
00:10:40,942 --> 00:10:41,823
than what we had planned.

249
00:10:42,243 --> 00:10:44,024
