258
00:11:00,374 --> 00:11:01,475
to help them find their way,

259
00:11:01,935 --> 00:11:04,176
to have more actionable items quicker,

260
00:11:04,637 --> 00:11:06,798
and then we would grow those into playthroughs,

261
00:11:06,978 --> 00:11:08,779
