264
00:11:14,243 --> 00:11:17,789
It's appropriate to use them as all the systems are converging and all the content's coming in.

265
00:11:18,190 --> 00:11:20,113
It's going to be buggy and messy as hell up front.

266
00:11:20,514 --> 00:11:24,320
And you want that team to feel a little bit of that pain, so then you can see day over day,

267
00:11:25,141 --> 00:11:28,086
it improves and you guys sort of uncover the hidden together and find the fun.

