270
00:11:34,500 --> 00:11:37,121
Crunch is big in the industry as producers

271
00:11:37,161 --> 00:11:39,502
and the owners of the time were responsible

272
00:11:39,722 --> 00:11:41,482
for the outcome of that if you do crunch.

273
00:11:42,203 --> 00:11:43,603
