292
00:12:19,479 --> 00:12:21,161
the recipient of everything that you've worked to build,

293
00:12:21,181 --> 00:12:22,724
and you want to maintain a relationship with them

294
00:12:22,764 --> 00:12:24,887
after you ship, especially in this day and age now, too,

295
00:12:24,907 --> 00:12:27,651
where there's more ways to communicate with them.

296
00:12:27,791 --> 00:12:28,853
