304
00:12:46,250 --> 00:12:48,131
It was just part of the informational process.

305
00:12:49,507 --> 00:12:51,811
So, these are XCOM's trust mechanics.

306
00:12:51,891 --> 00:12:54,055
Love the vision, love your support structure,

307
00:12:54,455 --> 00:12:55,337
and hear your community.

308
00:12:55,617 --> 00:12:57,761
These are ultimately what allowed us to light up our cave

309
00:12:58,001 --> 00:12:59,203
