00:33:32,138 --> 00:33:34,340
It wasn't like, oh, we had a big cut in scope here, or a

774
00:33:34,380 --> 00:33:36,861
big shift in decisions here, or priority

775
00:33:36,881 --> 00:33:37,862
changes from the client.

776
00:33:38,363 --> 00:33:41,245
It was like teams with really high morale were consistently

777
00:33:41,265 --> 00:33:44,066
pretty high, and they ebbed and flowed seemingly randomly.

