817
00:35:36,159 --> 00:35:39,603
But going through this process made it really clear to people

818
00:35:39,663 --> 00:35:41,664
on the team that there's a culture of being open to

819
00:35:41,704 --> 00:35:44,767
changing your mind, and people were very

