00:37:04,512 --> 00:37:07,333
And understanding how to simplify down to what was really important

848
00:37:07,653 --> 00:37:11,835
These were teams that would essentially actively market their vision in their team

849
00:37:12,395 --> 00:37:15,537
They wouldn't just write it in a Google Doc or bury it on Perforce.

850
00:37:15,757 --> 00:37:16,658
They would make posters.

851
00:37:16,698 --> 00:37:18,359
They would hang them up in the team areas.

852
00:37:19,200 --> 00:37:21,722
This became a marketing or propaganda effort for them to

853
00:37:21,742 --> 00:37:24,684
get everyone bought into that vision, which allowed a lot of

854
00:37:25,264 --> 00:37:28,807
really strong conversations of just, we have a lot of complex

