You're having a discussion about an upcoming release

1264
00:57:38,635 --> 00:57:41,317
for your game, it's a relatively healthy group discussion,

1265
00:57:41,357 --> 00:57:42,858
but your designer hasn't chimed in.

1266
00:57:43,678 --> 00:57:44,719
You ask them for their thoughts,

1267
00:57:45,200 --> 00:57:46,500
they kind of muddle through it,

1268
00:57:47,461 --> 00:57:48,802
you push them to clarify,

1269
00:57:49,323 --> 00:57:50,864
they say they'd prefer not to comment,

1270
00:57:51,304 --> 00:57:53,846
and you remind them that it is literally

1271
00:57:53,906 --> 00:57:56,848
their job description to have opinions about this feature.

1272
00:58:00,731 --> 00:58:01,632
Guess which one I was?

1273
00:58:03,593 --> 00:58:05,034
In this scenario, without knowing it,

1274
00:58:05,414 --> 00:58:06,375
I was a total bully.

1275
00:58:07,905 --> 00:58:08,666
I didn't know it.

1276
00:58:09,286 --> 00:58:10,067
I didn't mean to be.

1277
00:58:10,987 --> 00:58:13,809
Like I didn't, I think of myself as a rather gregarious dude.

1278
00:58:13,869 --> 00:58:15,130
I kind of try to be a little,

1279
00:58:15,410 --> 00:58:17,132
my wife calls me intensely laid back.

1280
00:58:21,815 --> 00:58:23,576
I thought I was the pretty girl in this picture.

1281
00:58:23,596 --> 00:58:24,677
I was not.

1282
00:58:25,457 --> 00:58:27,439
I goaded someone who was being quiet.

1283
00:58:27,539 --> 00:58:29,320
I prodded them when they felt intimidated.

1284
00:58:29,340 --> 00:58:32,962
I didn't allow their truth of intimidation to exist

1285
00:58:33,243 --> 00:58:34,003
because I didn't mean it.

1286
00:58:34,855 --> 00:58:37,176
It's like when I was little and my brother would hit me,

1287
00:58:37,976 --> 00:58:39,857
and it hurt, and he's like, I barely hit you.

1288
00:58:40,538 --> 00:58:41,238
We were both right.

1289
00:58:41,999 --> 00:58:43,920
He did barely hit me compared to what he could do,

1290
00:58:44,040 --> 00:58:46,301
but damn, he's four and a half years older than me,

1291
00:58:46,321 --> 00:58:48,382
he's like six foot two in the military, he's mean.

1292
00:58:49,103 --> 00:58:51,124
He hurt.

1293
00:58:53,165 --> 00:58:55,106
But it wasn't my intention, but my behavior that mattered.

1294
00:58:55,786 --> 00:58:57,687
And in their moment of vulnerability,

1295
00:58:58,268 --> 00:59:00,769
I met that with aggression and snark.

1296
00:59:05,259 --> 00:59:09,922
So I got pulled in by the founder of my company

1297
00:59:09,942 --> 00:59:12,383
and the HR manager that I was being threatening.

1298
00:59:14,925 --> 00:59:15,725
Phwoar.

1299
00:59:17,366 --> 00:59:19,468
Dude, that hurt.

1300
00:59:20,108 --> 00:59:21,769
And I wanted to make excuses,

1301
00:59:22,049 --> 00:59:23,530
and I had all the buts,

1302
00:59:23,730 --> 00:59:26,132
but it's his job, but it, but, but, but, no.

1303
00:59:28,793 --> 00:59:30,654
Somebody felt threatened by me.

1304
00:59:32,315 --> 00:59:32,776
I had to.

1305
00:59:34,157 --> 00:59:37,579
I had to feel the truth of that and think,

1306
00:59:38,220 --> 00:59:39,861
I'm a fucking bully.

1307
00:59:42,623 --> 00:59:43,444
And that hurt.

1308
00:59:45,165 --> 00:59:46,506
But I had to see that truth of it,

1309
00:59:46,546 --> 00:59:48,628
and I had to understand, and I had to process that

1310
00:59:48,668 --> 00:59:52,071
because it was important to how I treat people

1311
00:59:52,551 --> 00:59:54,112
and how I lead now.

1312
00:59:54,953 --> 00:59:56,574
This was an important thing for me to hear,

1313
00:59:56,614 --> 00:59:58,816
and I didn't love hearing it.

1314
01:00:00,626 --> 01:00:05,768
I'm going to leave you with some little snippet to remind myself to not be emotional about this anymore,

1315
01:00:06,608 --> 01:00:12,691
which is when you get into a position of leadership, the same discussion that you have,

1316
01:00:14,132 --> 01:00:17,733
the same words with the same person changes context and you have to be aware of that.

1317
01:00:18,854 --> 01:00:21,775
I wasn't aware of that and it's why I was being a bully essentially.

1318
01:00:22,275 --> 01:00:24,656
I would be able to have a discussion with somebody and go, that's kind of dumb.

1319
01:00:27,502 --> 01:00:28,202
Why would we do that?

1320
01:00:29,063 --> 01:00:30,304
Sometimes that would almost be like

1321
01:00:30,324 --> 01:00:32,285
a healthy conversation starter with your peers,

1322
01:00:33,326 --> 01:00:34,487
not so much when you're in charge.

1323
01:00:35,948 --> 01:00:37,970
Hey, that's dumb, sounds really dismissive.

1324
01:00:39,311 --> 01:00:40,732
Don't, I mean, don't do that anyway, but still.

1325
01:00:42,433 --> 01:00:42,633
So,

1326
01:00:46,556 --> 01:00:47,777
if you have the final say,

1327
01:00:49,138 --> 01:00:49,919
don't speak first.

1328
